  LLVM-COV: git clone http://llvm.org/git/llvm.git
  LCOV:     http://ltp.sourceforge.net/coverage/lcov.php
# install LCOV,  LLVM-COV using apt-get:
  $ sudo apt-get install lcov llvm

# How to use
 Create a build folder and jump into it:
  $ mkdir build && cd "$_"
 Run the script:
  $ facelift/tests/coverage_llvm-cov/test_llvm-cov.sh
 Results of coverage will be available in the folder
  $ llvm-cov/report_yy-mm-dd-hms
